3
2
text
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  KEY RULE:                                                   │
│                                                              │
│  MICROTASKS (Promises) ALWAYS execute before                 │
│  MACROTASKS (setTimeout) when both are waiting               │
│                                                              │
│  Priority: Synchronous > Microtask > Macrotask               │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

Example 3: Complex Event Loop
JavaScript
