MACROTASK PHASE (execute ONE macrotask):
  Execute cb1:
    console.log("2") → Print "2"
    Promise.resolve().then(cb4) → cb4 to microtask queue

MICROTASK PHASE (drain all microtasks again):
  Execute cb4:
    console.log("3") → Print "3"

MACROTASK PHASE (execute ONE macrotask):
  Execute cb3:
    console.log("5") → Print "5"

