┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  PROBLEMS WITH CALLBACKS                                     │
│                                                              │
│  1. Readability nightmare (horizontal pyramid)               │
│  2. Error handling at every level                            │
│  3. Inversion of control (you trust the callback caller)    │
│  4. Difficult to compose and reuse                          │
│  5. Hard to debug                                           │
│                                                              │
