│  SPREAD vs REST — Same syntax (...), different purpose       │
│                                                              │
│  SPREAD: Expands/unpacks elements                            │
│  REST: Collects/packs remaining elements                     │
│                                                              │
│  SPREAD = in function calls, arrays, objects (expanding)     │
│  REST = in function params, destructuring (collecting)       │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
