┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  OPTIONAL CHAINING (?.)                                      │
│                                                              │
│  Stops evaluation and returns undefined if left side is      │
│  null or undefined. Prevents "Cannot read property" errors.  │
│                                                              │
│  obj?.prop     → obj is null/undefined? → undefined          │
│  obj?.[expr]   → obj is null/undefined? → undefined          │
│  func?.()      → func is null/undefined? → undefined         │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

