// LIVE CODING SESSION: Build a Modal Component
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

/*
INTERVIEWER: "Build a reusable Modal component with:
1. Overlay backdrop
2. Close on escape and click outside
3. Focus trapping
4. Portal rendering
