        "Type guards and narrowing",
        "Utility types (Partial, Required, Pick, Omit)"
    ],

    webFundamentals: [
        "HTTP methods and status codes",
        "REST API design",
        "CORS and how it works",
        "Browser storage (localStorage, sessionStorage, cookies)",
        "Web security (XSS, CSRF)"
    ],

